/-!
# Fresh halving-based cotangent interval certificates for `11 ≤ k ≤ 12`

This file proves fresh rational interval bounds on `cotangentTermV a k` for the
coprime acute pairs `(a, k)` with `11 ≤ k ≤ 12` needed to discharge the
`cot_pi_a_k_bounds` axioms in `VasyuninPrimitiveBoundsCore.lean`, via the same
angle-doubling method as `CotangentBoundsK10.lean` (Taylor base case + `n`
doubling steps, `n` chosen automatically per pair so the resulting interval is
tight enough to imply the pre-declared rational bounds). The wrapper theorems
that actually replace the axioms live directly in `VasyuninPrimitiveBoundsCore.lean`
(editing the axiom lines in place), citing the lemmas proved here together with
the structural reductions from `CotangentBoundsCore.lean`.
-/

